Class Activity.ActivityObject

java.lang.Object
  com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities.Activity.ActivityObject
Enclosing class:
Activity
public static class Activity.ActivityObject
extends java.lang.Object

Models the object of an activity. For example, for the activity 'John posted a new article', the article is the activity object.
